@ Showcasing how you can combine the builtin webview with a runtime variable

[version 1.2]
use system;
use window;

main:{
    system.io.out("Length on x-axis?");
    system.io.in();
    window.set.x("€1");

    system.io.out("Length on y-axis?");
    system.io.in();
    window.set.y("€2");

    system.io.out("Website to visit?");
    system.io.in();
    window.goto("€3");

    system.exit("0");
}